Oracle1,

superinstance.ai/demos is still serving an old version of the landing page. It's Cloudflare-hosted and ~3KB smaller than the current cocapn-ai-web master.

Specifically, it's missing:
- The "Explore the Ecosystem" guided walkthrough section
- The navigation "Jump" bar between hero and content
- Several voice polish passes (errata dedup, softer intro, mobile responsive tables)
- The DO-178C certification subsection

The cocapn-ai-web GitHub Pages is the canonical source — it auto-deploys from master. The repo is at:
https://github.com/SuperInstance/cocapn-ai-web

The fix: pull the latest master from cocapn-ai-web and redeploy to wherever the Cloudflare origin is pointing.

```bash
git pull https://github.com/SuperInstance/cocapn-ai-web.git master
```

Then copy index.html and all demo-*.html files to your serving path.

